<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1042859' id='t-1042859'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:36
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1045785' id='t-1045785'>But the conductor doesn't make a sound.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1047810' id='t-1047810'>He depends, for his power,</span>
